title: New JFK murder theory
description:
New JFK murder theory

(PLEASE SEED! I'M SEEDING FROM A WEB CAFE AND CAN'T DO IT FOR VERY LONG!)

Newly released PDF scan of self-published book written by ex-agent of the US gov, says he knows who killed JFK. He says, and alleges to prove, that it was The John Birch Society in conjunction with the Mormon Church. 

Has photos of redacted documents, photos, I.D. cards, letters from J. Edgar Hoover, detailed descriptions, and much more. 

First chapter is autobiography and interesting life story and background of author. 

Second chapter is the "whodunnit" JFK part. 

In the last chapter of the book, the author says that after he self-published the first pressing of the book, his teenaged son was murdered as retaliation for publishing the book. 

(book split into two PDFs due to limitations of scanner)
